Package cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.language.nodes.call

Package contains nodes that take care of invoking subroutines and assigning values passed as arguments to their corresponding variables defined in subroutine heading.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InvokeNode
    Node representing invocation of a subroutine.
    ReadAllArgumentsNode
    This node is used to read all arguments from actual frame and return them.
    ReadArgumentNode
    This node reads one argument from actual frame at specified index.
    ReferenceInitializationNode
    This node is used to initialize reference passed variable in called subroutine.
    UnitInvokeNode
    Node representing invocation of a subroutine from unit.
